Note on the demos: the HTML specimens in fonts/*.html reference JetBrains Mono
(fonts/fallback/) purely as a Cyrillic fallback for preview. JetBrains Mono is
licensed under the SIL Open Font License 1.1 and is NOT embedded into any
Comic True Mono output file — it is only used for on-screen preview. If the
demos are redistributed with that file, include its OFL license.
